name: Young Thug
description: The emotion and layer that Young Thug displays in his music shows not only meticulous creation but depth of thought.

name: Travis Scott
description: The production value of Travis Scott's music outmatches any of his competitors.

name: Drake
description: Drake displays range as a rapper, r&b singer, spanish singer and much much more, things his competitors can't do.

name: Juice Wrld
description: At 19 years old, Juice Wrld displays some of the rawest natural talent the industry has ever seen.

name: Future
description: Future is a machine, it is rumored that he is capable of making an entire album in one day…and he has.
